Help! Help!

25:08.637 --> 25:11.335
-Help! Help!
-Get off of him!

25:11.379 --> 25:12.423
Stop! It's me!

25:12.467 --> 25:14.382
Emily! What the hell
are you doing?

25:14.425 --> 25:17.341
