35:38.005 --> 35:39.224
Don't do it.

36:30.318 --> 36:31.363
LIZ: Eli?

36:33.060 --> 36:34.366
Eli.

36:35.367 --> 36:37.238
-Eli!
-Yeah?

36:37.282 --> 36:39.632
-Excuse me?
-Yes?

36:39.675 --> 36:43.766
Video games, laptop,
any electronic thingamajig
goes in this bin.

36:43.810 --> 36:46.726
-Right now?
-Yeah. Right now.
Hop to it.

37:34.164 --> 37:36.297
LIZ: Eli, hurry up.
I don't have all day.

37:37.124 --> 37:38.517
ELI: Coming!

37:40.519 --> 37:42.303
-RICHARD: No.
I don't hate him.

37:42.347 --> 37:43.826
I actually like him.

37:43.870 --> 37:46.351
Problem is
he reminds me of me
when I was his age.

37:47.134 --> 37:48.440
That's what scares me.

37:49.354 --> 37:51.443
Dominic's
a safe driver, okay?

37:51.486 --> 37:53.749
RICHARD: If I can hear it
a mile down the road,
you shouldn't be riding in it.

37:54.576 --> 37:57.187
-Hey, buddy.
-EMILY: Heads up.

37:57.231 --> 37:58.841
I don't know what
you slipped Sam,

37:58.885 --> 38:02.105
