38:04.282 --> 38:05.370
EMILY: I got your favorite.

38:05.413 --> 38:06.762
Vanilla caramel fudge.

38:08.198 --> 38:10.200
Why are you
being nice to me?

38:10.244 --> 38:11.680
Because I love you.

38:14.379 --> 38:16.076
What's going on?

38:16.119 --> 38:18.383
Your mother and I
are going out tonight,

38:18.426 --> 38:22.169
and Emily has agreed
that she's going to
stay here and babysit,

38:22.212 --> 38:23.823
because it's part
of her punishment.

38:24.519 --> 38:25.955
EMILY: It'll be fun.

38:25.999 --> 38:28.654
We'll watch a movie
or something.
I don't know.

38:28.697 --> 38:30.656
Figure out what
you want to do.
I'm gonna go shower.

38:32.788 --> 38:35.530
She actually bought you
an ice cream.

38:35.574 --> 38:37.053
It's gotta be
a record or something.

38:37.097 --> 38:38.707
You can't leave me
alone with her.

38:38.751 --> 38:39.839
She's gonna kill me.

38:39.882 --> 38:41.710
Nobody's going to
kill you, bud.

38:41.754 --> 38:42.842
Nobody.

38:42.885 --> 38:44.931
What have I
told you about girls?

38:44.974 --> 38:46.149
That they're crazy.

38:46.193 --> 38:48.064
Yeah.

38:48.108 --> 38:51.938
And you really think I'm
going to leave you home alone
with Mrs. Burghly?

38:52.678 --> 38:55.550
No. I called Dominic.

38:55.594 --> 38:58.205
He's gonna come
and "babysit" Emily.

38:58.248 --> 38:59.772
-Really?
-Yeah.

38:59.815 --> 39:02.383
But I don't want any
funny business tonight.

39:02.427 --> 39:04.429
You're my eyes
and ears, okay?

39:04.472 --> 39:06.213
You gotta keep
an eye on him.

39:06.256 --> 39:07.997
I will. Dominic's awesome.

39:09.042 --> 39:11.087
He's okay. Are we good?

39:12.524 --> 39:13.873
That a boy.

39:13.916 --> 39:15.614
Make sure you eat your
ice cream before it melts.

39:16.571 --> 39:18.704
-Hey, Dad?
-Yeah.

39:18.747 --> 39:20.662
Mom's a girl.
Is she crazy?

39:40.987 --> 39:43.816
Dad, can you buy me
a generator?

41:08.291 --> 41:11.469
RICHARD: I mean, come on.
Another night of video games
isn't gonna hurt anybody.

41:11.512 --> 41:12.992
LIZ: You're such a pushover.

41:13.035 --> 41:14.428
RICHARD: By the way,
you look hot tonight.

41:14.472 --> 41:16.735
-Wow, Mom. You look amazing.

41:16.778 --> 41:19.433
"Wow, Mom"?
What about me?

41:19.477 --> 41:20.913
You look like
you're going to work.

41:22.741 --> 41:23.959
Thanks.

41:24.003 --> 41:25.700
Do you have
your phone, big guy?

41:27.485 --> 41:28.660
Okay, good.
Remember what I said.

41:28.703 --> 41:30.444
If Emily acts up,
you let me know.

41:30.488 --> 41:32.794
In case of emergency,
you go to Mr. Hynous' house.

41:32.838 --> 41:34.840
But Mr. Hynous hates people.

41:34.883 --> 41:37.451
Mr. Hynous
doesn't hate people,
just little kids.

41:39.627 --> 41:43.631
But you are my eyes
and ears tonight.

41:44.197 --> 41:45.285
Right?

41:45.851 --> 41:47.113
Good boy.

41:47.156 --> 41:48.897
I'm too young
to be a grandfather.

41:48.941 --> 41:50.377
LIZ: Come on, let's go.
We're gonna be late.

41:50.986 --> 41:52.205
