42:31.505 --> 42:32.724
Yeah.

42:32.767 --> 42:34.552
I'm sorry I chickened out.

42:35.161 --> 42:36.728
It's okay.

42:36.771 --> 42:39.165
It's just that I felt
what was down there,

42:39.208 --> 42:41.907
and that was way worse
than being scared.

42:42.647 --> 42:43.996
Now do you believe me?

42:44.039 --> 42:45.563
Yeah.

42:45.606 --> 42:49.175
But don't worry, Eli.
We're gonna
do this together.

42:49.218 --> 42:52.874
