she's half zombie, right?

43:44.534 --> 43:45.535
Yeah.

43:47.494 --> 43:48.930
But she's a cute zombie.

43:50.192 --> 43:52.630
Is this one new?
I haven't played
this one before.

43:52.673 --> 43:54.849
Yeah. It's epic,
but I suck at it.

43:54.893 --> 43:56.372
-I can't figure out...
-Wow.

43:57.939 --> 43:59.201
Wow. Uh...

44:00.507 --> 44:02.117
I, uh...

44:02.161 --> 44:03.989
I thought we were just
chillin' here tonight?

44:04.032 --> 44:06.295
I'm gonna call Mom,
and you're gonna be
grounded forever.

44:06.339 --> 44:10.125
Mom and Dad are crazy
if they think I'm wasting
a Saturday night on you.

44:15.740 --> 44:16.784
Sam, help!

44:16.828 --> 44:17.872
DOMINIC: Emily!

44:20.875 --> 44:22.398
EMILY: Game over, loser.

44:23.922 --> 44:25.184
SAM:  Eli?

44:26.707 --> 44:27.752
You okay, buddy?

44:32.408 --> 44:33.671
SAM: Eli?

44:33.714 --> 44:35.629
Now, you stay here
and keep your mouth shut,

44:35.673 --> 44:37.805
or I'm really gonna
make your life a living hell.

44:51.471 --> 44:54.213
Hey, he's just a kid.
We can't leave him here.

44:54.256 --> 44:59.218
You can stay here
and babysit if you want.
I'm leaving.

45:03.004 --> 45:04.484
It's just a few hours.

45:05.964 --> 45:08.009
I'll make it up to you.
I'll come by tomorrow.

45:08.053 --> 45:09.402
We'll go for a ride
in the Firebreather.

45:10.620 --> 45:11.752
Sound good?

45:11.796 --> 45:12.840
Let's go.

45:20.892 --> 45:21.980
Be good.

45:24.069 --> 45:28.160
Or the man downstairs
might pay you a visit.

46:52.026 --> 46:53.593
VOICE:
Golem bash.

48:45.661 --> 48:48.099
ELI: Mr. Hynous!
Mr. Hynous!

48:48.969 --> 48:50.623
Mr. Hynous!

48:50.666 --> 48:52.451
Mr. Hynous!

48:52.494 --> 48:54.105
Mr. Hynous!

48:54.148 --> 48:56.324
-MAN: Get the fuck outta
the middle of the road.

49:15.604 --> 49:18.129
Quickly. After that
submersible. Yah!

49:20.087 --> 49:22.176
MAN:
Hey, hey, hey, buddy.
How's it goin' there?

49:22.220 --> 49:24.831
So listen. Me and the guys
here have been talking,

49:24.874 --> 49:29.792
and, well, there's no real
easy way of puttin' this,
but, uh...

49:29.836 --> 49:31.316
We're kicking you
out of the ocean, bitch.

49:59.692 --> 50:01.781
We gotta go
get this walkie, buddy.

50:07.526 --> 50:09.180
-Good night, my love.
-Good night.

50:10.398 --> 50:12.922
And now I lay me
down to sleep.

50:12.966 --> 50:14.924
I pray the Lord
my soul to keep.

50:15.838 --> 50:17.362
If I die before I wake,

50:17.405 --> 50:19.407
I pray the Lord
my soul to take.

50:59.969 --> 51:01.971
ELI:
Hot Rod, watch my back,

51:02.015 --> 51:04.148
and make sure
the door stays open.

51:07.325 --> 51:08.761
My light is strong.

51:09.892 --> 51:11.981
My light is strong.

51:12.025 --> 51:13.548
My light is strong.

51:41.968 --> 51:44.013
Where is it?

51:51.673 --> 51:53.110
My light is strong.

51:54.198 --> 51:55.590
My light is strong.

51:56.200 --> 51:57.853
My light is strong.

52:02.336 --> 52:03.816
It should be right here.

52:04.817 --> 52:06.732
Come on.
Where are you?

52:14.131 --> 52:16.002
He's gonna wake up.
Come on.

53:26.986 --> 53:28.117
Whoa!

55:22.406 --> 55:23.407
